{"tid":1007472,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"人越大越唔想強調自己幾叻，有咩skill，同其他人有咩唔同","createTime":"2019-02-03T19:06:04.000Z","updateTime":"2019-02-03T20:45:17.000Z","uid":58316,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"c871cbbc07a8bc12cdfc76adba94133304c4473a","tid":1007472,"uid":58316,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-03T19:06:04.000Z","msg":"返工好似玩咁<br />\n打牙骹<br />\n有糧出過日晨算<br />\n生活可以話有重心<br />\n又可以話冇<br />\n以前成日好想stand out<br />\n而家已經唔諗<br />\n進唔進修<br />\n係咪讀返書<br />\ncareer path點行<br />\n由細到大d cert<br />\n全部收埋哂<br />\n人大左<br />\n只想揾安全感<br />\n甘於平淡<br />\n因為原來<br />\n平淡都唔係理所當然<br />\n唔係話你想要就有<br />\n返工<br />\n揾返一萬幾千<br />\n着衫<br />\n人着乜我着乜<br />\n大路公廁款<br />\n聽歌<br />\n電台播咩聽咩<br />\n好似一陣風咁生存<br />\n吹過就算<br />\n淡淡交會過<br />\n各不留下印"},{"pid":"9540788f16ba8b42791451d3f45722228162ba9c","tid":1007472,"uid":183752,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-03T19:09:53.000Z","msg":"係咁加啦。<br />\n一事無成。<br />\n唔通無樣叻。<br />\n又爭住叻咩。<br />\n出到黎做野就會知。<br />\n你做到人地都做到。<br />\n平淡就唔係我地想既。<br />\n只係無得選擇先平淡。"},{"pid":"0890cd6bf021cf3426f024f2b79e554928dc7d8a","tid":1007472,"uid":13281,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-03T20:45:17.000Z","msg":"Everyone you will ever meet knows something you don&rsquo;t<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/smile2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/smile2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}